These are Puzzles for 1x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-1-1::.
5 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, rabbit, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |    2     |     3      |   4    |      5       |
| Pet   | bird | ferret | rabbit | rat | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-1-2::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, skateboard, helicopter, car
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |   5    |
| Transport   | helicopter | car | quad-bike | trike | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-1-3::.
