.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, folk, dubstep, d&b, hip-hop
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |  1   |   2    |     3      |      4      |   5    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | d&b | hip-hop | dubstep | reggae |

