.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-1-16::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, december, july, september, november
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |  2   |   3    |   4    |  5  |
| Birthday   | december | april | september | july | november |

